            "creation_date": 1376376872,
            "body": "<p>I tried here in my computer this way and works fine<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>PreparedStatement pt =con.prepareStatement(\"DELETE FROM users  WHERE IF EXISTS user_name='\"+\"example'\");\npt.executeUpdate();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>I made a temporary table and run it<\/p>\n",
